episodes.title: Clean Slate
episodes.plot: Franky fights to prove her innocence, while the aftermath of the escape drives the staff into conflict.

episodes.title: The Boxer
episodes.plot: Franky finds the evidence she was seeking and acts on it. Ruby is recruited into fighting against her will. Allie learns some new information. Jake makes an unexpected decision about how to move forward with Vera.

episodes.title: Bleed Out
episodes.plot: After being shot Franky seeks Bridget's help but the police net is tightening and time is running out. Meanwhile, Kaz faces her toughest challenge when she warns Kosta to stop fight club, but that doesn't stop Ruby from fighting.

episodes.title: Winter Is Here
episodes.plot: Marie Winter arrives; Sonia makes a deal with Vera and the workshop is reopened. Will cracks under pressure as he confesses to Jake that he buried Joan alive.

episodes.title: Bitter Pill
episodes.plot: When Jake saves Liz's life in a selfless act, Vera is forced to reassess her opinion of him.

episodes.title: Angel of Wentworth
episodes.plot: As Sonia tries to spin her 'Angel of Wentworth' PR into an innocence campaign, her past crimes threaten to derail her - and it could be fatal.

episodes.title: The Edge
episodes.plot: When Sonia is refused entry into Protection, she goes on the attack, setting up a plan to discredit Kaz's position as Top Dog. With Marie onside, they set a scheme in motion, which may have drastic repercussions for Allie.

episodes.title: Lovers and Fighters
episodes.plot: Ruby's personal information becomes knowledge and Allie convinces her to play it safe. Meanwhile Marie has a lead on who killed her son.

episodes.title: Shallow Grave
episodes.plot: Will unburdens his problem to Vera, but still loses it. Boomer decides to fight in a boxing match. Rita plays a dangerous game over her cover with Marie. Jake, Will and Vera make a decision.

episodes.title: Fractured
episodes.plot: Marie discovers that Liz may have witnessed the attack on Cherry Li and tries to protect her from Drago. Meanwhile, Vera, Will and Jake face a blackmail threat - someone else knows the dark secret they are protecting.

episodes.title: Indelible Ink
episodes.plot: Drago discovers the truth behind Marie's son's death, as a disgraced Channing tries to manipulate Vera and Will into giving him his old job as governor back.

episodes.title: Showdown
episodes.plot: The police close in on Vera, Will and Jake. While Rita takes drastic action to protect her sister.
